Package: cv2r
Title: Use OpenCV in RStudio 
Version: 0.5.1
Author: Emmanuel BATT [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Emmanuel BATT <emmanuel.batt.cran@battfamily.fr>
Authors@R: person("Emmanuel", "BATT", email = "emmanuel.batt.cran@battfamily.fr", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: All it does is to import cv2 from python through reticulate and overload imshow so that the output can be visualised in the Viewer pane.
Depends: R (>= 3.4.0)
